2. Flipping the matrix:

n = len(matrix)

    s = 0

    for i in range(n//2):

        for j in range(n//2):

            s += max(matrix[i][j], matrix[i][n-j-1], matrix[n-i-1][j], matrix[n-i-1][n-j-1])

    return s


